  "privacy.title": "Privacy Policy",
  "privacy.last_updated": "Last updated: March 2026",
  "privacy.intro_title": "1. Introduction",
  "privacy.intro_text": "Welcome to DevBoards.io. We are committed to protecting your personal data and respecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and share your data when you use our platform.",
  "privacy.collection_title": "2. Data We Collect",
  "privacy.collection_text": "We collect information you provide directly (such as account details, profile information, CV data), data from third parties (e.g., when you log in via GitHub/LinkedIn/Google), and usage data (logs, device info).",
  "privacy.usage_title": "3. How We Use Your Data",
  "privacy.usage_text": "We use your data to provide our services, match you with job opportunities, improve our platform, and communicate with you. We do not sell your personal data to third parties.",
  "privacy.sharing_title": "4. Data Sharing",
  "privacy.sharing_text": "We may share your data with prospective employers when you apply for a job, with service providers who help us operate our platform, or when required by law.",
  "privacy.security_title": "5. Data Security",
  "privacy.security_text": "We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.",
  "privacy.rights_title": "6. Your Rights",
  "privacy.rights_text": "Under GDPR and other applicable laws, you have the right to access, correct, delete, or restrict the processing of your data. You can manage most settings directly in your profile.",
  "privacy.cookies_title": "7. Cookies",
  "privacy.cookies_text": "We use only strictly necessary technical cookies for platform operation: session authentication and preferred language storage. For traffic analysis we use Microsoft Clarity in cookieless mode (no tracking cookies). We do not use profiling or marketing cookies. See our Cookie Policy for the full list.",
  "privacy.contact_title": "8. Contact Us",
  "privacy.contact_text": "If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us at privacy@devboards.io.",
  "footer.privacy_policy": "Privacy Policy",
